  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You&rsquo;ve seen the horrors of war, and had hoped you&rsquo;d seen the end of it. You&rsquo;ve retreated from the fighting&mdash;likely from the front line with Molthune, but maybe from the crusade of Lastwall or the political infighting of Ustalav&mdash;and now just want to protect and provide for those you care about.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You gain one of the following as a permanent class skill: Appraise, Heal, Knowledge (history), Sense Motive, or Survival. When you perform an aid another action to improve a creature&rsquo;s Armor Class, you increase its AC by +4 rather than +2.</span></p>",
